gomodel:SYNGO_3809  a     owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: Fig.1: \"In vivo two photon time lapse imaging in adolescent and young adult Lis1+/+ and Lis1+/- mice.\"\n- \"Significant decreases occurred in turnover and elimination rates of filopodia in Lis1+/- animals over 10 min (Fig 1A and B, Supporting Information Fig 1A). \"\n\nFig.2: \"Downregulation of RhoA in Lis1+/- neurons rescues motility in a subset of filopodia.\"\n\nFig.4: \"Reduced spine density in young pyramidal neurons of Lis1+/- mice.\". Experimental description: - M&M: \"Mice Animals ..\"" ;
        lego:modelstate   "production" ;
        dc:contributor    "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-2514-0216" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-2286-1587" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0003-0593-3443" ;
